<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Huzifa - Forex Trading</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000 0%, #001a4d 50%, #000 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(0, 26, 77, 0.9);
            border: 2px solid #0066cc;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.3);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .profile-img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid #0066cc;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            object-fit: cover;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.5);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.3);
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #0066cc;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .links-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .link-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066cc 0%, #003d7a 100%);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            border: 2px solid #00aaff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.3);
        }

        .link-btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00aaff 0%, #0066cc 100%);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 170, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .telegram-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0088cc 0%, #005fa3 100%);
            border-color: #00ddff;
        }

        .telegram-btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00ddff 0%, #0088cc 100%);
        }

        .register-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #003d7a 0%, #001a4d 100%);
            border-color: #0066cc;
        }

        .register-btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066cc 0%, #003d7a 100%);
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #0066cc;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            .profile-img {
                width: 120px;
                height: 120px;
            }

            .link-btn {
                padding: 12px 20px;
                font-size: 1em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="profile.jpg" alt="Huzifa" class="profile-img">
        <h1>Huzifa</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">📈 متداول فوركس منذ 3 سنوات</p>

        <div class="links-container">
            <a href="https://t.me/HASKAWI_TRADING" class="link-btn telegram-btn" target="_blank">
                <span class="icon">✈️</span>توصيات مجانية على التليجرام
            </a>

            <a href="https://one.justmarkets.link/a/tuu6hv0s86" class="link-btn register-btn" target="_blank">
                <span class="icon">🚀</span>سجل تحت وكالتي
            </a>
        </div>

        <p class="footer">💙 محترف في مجال الفوركس</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
